tab-stops:21.3pt 35.45pt 411.1pt;layout-grid-mode:char&quot;&gt;Prior to the occupation of the development,
notwithstanding site investigation and clearance works and demolition, full
details relating to the following shall be submitted to and approved by the
Local Planning Authority: a)&amp;nbsp; The design
of secure and lockable cycle stores, b)&amp;nbsp;
Refuse and recycling facilities, c)&amp;nbsp;
All forms of external lighting to be provided on site. The development
shall be carried out fully in accordance with the approved details prior to
first occupation of the development and shall be thereafter maintained as such
for the lifetime of the development.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

